headline: Tariffs are starting to squeeze profits for Trump-loving farmers
summary: (Bloomberg) -- President Donald Trump has repeatedly said he loves farmers. headline: Mosaic: A Strong Foundation, But Not A Buy (For Now)
summary: Mosaic is a major fertilizer producer with a strong foundation, but its profitability is highly dependent on the volatile commodity cycle. See why MOS stock is a Hold.
